stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PROVISIONING
    PROVISIONING --> PROVISIONED : AWS running
    PROVISIONING --> TERMINATED : AWS terminated
    PROVISIONED --> CONFIGURING : cloud-init starts
    CONFIGURING --> CONFIGURED : cloud-init done
    CONFIGURING --> CONFIGURING_FAILED : cloud-init error
    CONFIGURING_FAILED --> CONFIGURING : retry
    CONFIGURED --> DEPLOYING : SSH deploy initiated
    DEPLOYING --> DEPLOYED : agent binary installed
    DEPLOYING --> DEPLOYING_FAILED : SSH/install error
    DEPLOYING_FAILED --> DEPLOYING : retry
    DEPLOYED --> REGISTERING : WebSocket open
    REGISTERING --> REGISTERED : Register validated
    REGISTERING --> REGISTERING_FAILED : timeout
    REGISTERING_FAILED --> REGISTERING : retry
    REGISTERED --> ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT : first heartbeat
    ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT --> AWAITING_HEARTBEAT : heartbeat due
    AWAITING_HEARTBEAT --> ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT : heartbeat received
    ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT --> LOST_HEARTBEAT : 30s silence
    AWAITING_HEARTBEAT --> LOST_HEARTBEAT : 30s silence
    LOST_HEARTBEAT --> REGISTERING : agent reconnects
    LOST_HEARTBEAT --> ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT : heartbeat received
    PROVISIONING --> TERMINATED
    CONFIGURING --> TERMINATED
    DEPLOYING --> TERMINATED
    REGISTERING --> TERMINATED
    REGISTERED --> TERMINATED
    ACTIVE_HEARTBEAT --> TERMINATED
    LOST_HEARTBEAT --> TERMINATED
    TERMINATED --> [*]
